OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1779279069
OL,3,CLifeline veterans charity turning to
OL,4,Cgreen energy in fight to keep lights on
OL,6,FA veterans charity which provides a
OL,7,Flifeline to former servicemen and
OL,8,Fwomen in the North East is turning to
OL,9,Fgreen energy in its fight to keep the
OL,10,Flights on.
OL,12,FMorgan House in Boosbeck, near Redcar,
OL,13,Fhouses up to 32 veterans and is aiming
OL,14,Fto raise enough funds to install solar
OL,15,Fpanels so it can mitigate against what
OL,16,Fit has labelled as the "astronomical"
OL,17,Felectricity bills it currently pays.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1779279069
OL,3,CLifeline veterans charity turning to
OL,4,Cgreen energy in fight to keep lights on
OL,6,FThe facility is completely reliant on
OL,7,Fgrid electricity, with no access to
OL,8,Fmains gas and staff at the hub are
OL,9,Fconcerned about the impact the current
OL,10,Fconflict in the Middle East could have
OL,11,Fon its energy costs.
OL,13,FAndrew Powell, from the charity
OL,14,FHealthier Heroes, which runs the site,
OL,15,Ftold ITV News Tyne Tees: "What's going
OL,16,Fon in Iran there at the minute, it's
OL,17,Fgoing to massively affect us I think.
OL,18,FAt the minute we're on #7,500 a month
OL,19,Ffor electricity.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1779279069
OL,3,CLifeline veterans charity turning to
OL,4,Cgreen energy in fight to keep lights on
OL,6,F"The building's reliant on it. With
OL,7,Fthe price cap and the energy increase
OL,8,Fand all that, you know, I think it's
OL,9,Fgoing to be astronomical, the bills
OL,10,Fthat we're going to end up paying I
OL,11,Fthink.
OL,13,F"I certainly would never close it, but
OL,14,Fwhat it would mean is that we'd need
OL,15,Fto do additional fundraising, grant
OL,16,Ffunding, we'd have to work so hard to
OL,17,Ftry and, obviously, get the money in
OL,18,Fand pay for the bills."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42604
