CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1779279069
OL,3,CLifeline veterans charity turning to
OL,4,Cgreen energy in fight to keep lights on
OL,6,FForecasts suggest an increase of
OL,7,Faround 13 to 18 per cent for typical
OL,8,Fdual-fuel households due to soaring
OL,9,Fwholesale gas costs.
OL,11,FMorgan House opened in November 2025
OL,12,Fand was named after Sam Morgan from
OL,13,FGuisborough, a Royal Marine
OL,14,FAfghanistan veteran who suffered from
OL,15,Fdepression and PTSD for years before
OL,16,Ftaking his own life in 2024.
OL,18,FHis family and friends are now
OL,19,Ffundraising to help mitigate the
OL,20,Fenergy costs Morgan House faces, with
OL,21,Fthe aim of installing solar panels.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1779279069
OL,3,CLifeline veterans charity turning to
OL,4,Cgreen energy in fight to keep lights on
OL,6,FSam's friend, Chris Hankinson, said:
OL,7,F"There is a bit of a goal that we've
OL,8,Fgot in mind, to try and get some solar
OL,9,Fpanels in place for Morgan House that
OL,10,Fshould massively reduce the reliance
OL,11,Fon the grid electric.
OL,13,F"We've been speaking with businesses
OL,14,Fin the area that provide these types
OL,15,Fof products and services and they're
OL,16,Fconfident that within a very short
OL,17,Fspace of time, they could reduce the
OL,18,Fbills by up to 33 per cent initially."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1779279069
OL,3,CLifeline veterans charity turning to
OL,4,Cgreen energy in fight to keep lights on
OL,6,FDespite only being operational for six
OL,7,Fmonths, Morgan House has already had a
OL,8,Fpositive impact on veterans' lives.
OL,10,FJason Young is an RAF veteran and when
OL,11,Fhe was referred to the service last
OL,12,FChristmas Eve, he described himself as
OL,13,Fsuicidal.
OL,15,FHe said: "I was on the brink of
OL,16,Fsuicide when I come here. I was at the
OL,17,Fdoor of it. I had nothing left,
OL,18,Fnowhere else to go, it saved my life
OL,19,Fbasically. I dread to think what would
OL,20,Fhave happened another week, if it had
OL,21,Fbeen a week later.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1779279069
OL,3,CLifeline veterans charity turning to
OL,4,Cgreen energy in fight to keep lights on
OL,6,F"I kept falling back into substance
OL,7,Fmisuse and I had a lot of stress, and
OL,8,Fit leads to nothing in the end, you
OL,9,Flose your friends, your family, you
OL,10,Flose your home, and that's what led me
OL,11,Fhere, so it was just by luck...
OL,13,F"I was just there on the right day,
OL,14,Fwith the right guy and he knew about
OL,15,Fthis place and he made a phone call,
OL,16,Fand that was Christmas Eve last year.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,427,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F426A1779279069
OL,3,CLifeline veterans charity turning to
OL,4,Cgreen energy in fight to keep lights on
OL,6,F"I get quite emotional even thinking
OL,7,Fabout it. I've had time to focus on
OL,8,Fthe stuff I've not dealt with in my
OL,9,Flife and tried to put measures in and
OL,10,Fthe counselling and what not."
OL,12,FVeterans who are referred to the hub
OL,13,Fare given an holistic package of
OL,14,Fsupport over two years, including
OL,15,Fhousing, heating, food, drug and
OL,16,Frehabilitation outreach programmes and
OL,17,Feducation.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
